data.text: S1 E9: The Goblin returns and figures out that Spider-Man is Peter Parker. They are both then kidnapped by Rejects, failed Beastials created by the High Evolutionary. They attempt to sneak into one of the Evoltuionary's hideouts so Spider-Man can escape, pretending to help the Rejects.
